Ilsa!

1430
02:03:41,275 --> 02:03:42,372
Benji!

1431
02:03:42,374 --> 02:03:43,506
Benji!

1432
02:03:43,508 --> 02:03:45,308
Ilsa, cô ở đâu?

1433
